":68,"year":"1328","julianDay":2206102,"title":"First War of Scottish Independence","description":"The First War of Scottish Independence began after England invaded Scotland in 1296. The Treaty of Edinburgh was signed in 1328 which declared peace between the two kingdoms and brought the war to an end.","jurisdictionLevel":0}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs Peter Oldcastle was born about 1260, in England. She had at least 1 son with Peter Oldcastle."},"et":{"about 1260–":"umbes 1260–Surnud","1255–1297":"1255–1297","1284–1310":"1284–1310","1260–Female":"1260–Surnud","about 1260":"umbes 1260","1315":"1315","1310":"1310","1255":"1255","1297":"1297","1284":"1284","1260":"1260","1328":"1328","1317":"1317","1290":"1290","England":"England","Almeley, Herefordshire, England":"Almeley, Herefordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1260–":"noin 1260–Kuollut","1255–1297":"1255–1297","1284–1310":"1284–1310","1260–Female":"1260–Kuollut","about 1260":"noin 1260","1315":"1315","1310":"1310","1255":"1255","1297":"1297","1284":"1284","1260":"1260","1328":"1328","1317":"1317","1290":"1290","England":"England","Almeley, Herefordshire, England":"Almeley, Herefordshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1260–":"environ 1260–Décédée","1255–1297":"1255–1297","1284–1310":"1284–1310","1260–Female":"1260–Décédée","about 1260":"environ 1260","1315":"1315","1310":"1310","1255":"1255","1297":"1297","1284":"1284","1260":"1260","1328":"1328","1317":"1317","1290":"1290","England":"Angleterre","Almeley, Herefordshire, England":"Almeley, Herefordshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Mrs Peter Oldcastle est née environ 1260, à Angleterre. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Peter Oldcastle."},"de":{"about 1260–":"um 1260–Verstorben","1255–1297":"1255–1297","1284–1310":"1284–1310","1260–Female":"1260–Verstorben","about 1260":"um 1260","1315":"1315","1310":"1310","1255":"1255","1297":"1297","1284":"1284","1260":"1260","1328":"1328","1317":"1317","1290":"1290","England":"England","Alme